{"tid":1304994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣撚入]普及政治,有無得諗?","createTime":"2019-07-10T18:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T19:22:31.000Z","uid":212336,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"71696942599df8835573f5f57b9f3159ef3bfc3a","tid":1304994,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:06:45.000Z","msg":"個人唔主張去說服啲廢老,但其實我發現好多後生既都幾戇鳩,成日覺得事不關己,呢班友直頭睇字都懶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我地有無辦法導入科普既概念,將時事政治簡化到容易入口切身既比喻,又不失核心,務求令到盲字都唔識既人都知發生緊咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">科學普及，簡稱科普，又稱大眾科學、流行科學（英語：popular science）或者普及科學，是指利用各種傳媒以淺顯的方式向普通大眾普及科學技術知識，倡導科學方法、傳播科學思想、弘揚科學精神的活動。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"99af45ee9068992054c314ae348da4d5af497bf1","tid":1304994,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:11:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d58713265734b2f86faea5d8d010d5309abb0ef8","tid":1304994,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:12:01.000Z","msg":"一、<span style=\"color: gold;\">撤銷反送中抗爭者控罪 </span><br />\n二、<span style=\"color: gold;\">成立獨立調查委員會追究警方濫權 </span><br />\n三、<span style=\"color: gold;\">實行真雙普選 </span><br />\n四、撤回引渡條例修訂草案<br />\n五、撤回6.12暴動定義<br />\n六、要求永不實行「社會信用評分系統」<br />\n七、徹回「多功能監控系統」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n香港人 永不放棄<br />\n長期抗爭呀！！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: red;\">請FOCUS返主線</span> <br />\n睇內文 要FACT CHECK <br />\n勿分化 不割蓆<br />\n唔好推膠post<br />\n整圖做文宣 air drop 俾其他市民<br />\n簽聯署<br />\n出活動要保護自己<br />\n唔好做沙包</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3aeba8cca2b5b265619d13b1292280fd10b7df","tid":1304994,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94e3b4f04b2ab4bb62855ad307faf88680506936","tid":1304994,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:25:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8bc43f648e4141321457cceafa2a95bcff4dbe1","tid":1304994,"uid":104676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:28:30.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有得諗 依排我都諗緊點樣將啲事變得易入口啲<br />\n覺得有啲文宣好詳細 但太多字懶得睇既人係會直接skip"},{"pid":"7707a40722a853bb7a6391a24e6e2a0bfb870a4e","tid":1304994,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:30:32.000Z","msg":"廢老/廢中：民主可以當飯食？無自由又點？你睇美國，就係咁樣先咁亂！<br />\n<br />\n點樣用100字解釋&amp;反駁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fd2f50e465d1ab94a119eafc3591032956880b","tid":1304994,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8bc43f648e4141321457cceafa2a95bcff4dbe1","tid":1304994,"uid":104676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:28:30.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有得諗 依排我都諗緊點樣將啲事變得易入口啲<br />\n覺得有啲文宣好詳細 但太多字懶得睇既人係會直接skip"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:34:49.000Z","msg":"簡單切身既比喻同,我覺得除咗易明之外,對方都無咁易起鋼,同時又要令佢知到關佢自己事<br />\n<br />\n好似屯門單嘢咁,你要同啲師奶講每日百五個有咩唔好?<br />\n<br />\n「每日百五隻雞落黎搵食,你老公咪去屯門叫雞囉,點解會有呢啲事發生?香港政府囉」"},{"pid":"72966000fc1900873cf63552f035498826679b74","tid":1304994,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:35:22.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"743c8e11ce8a370b0f4a4e5037aefa428ced3845","tid":1304994,"uid":277159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:38:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"028af440e55006e0fa9bf361123d432c2afd1495","tid":1304994,"uid":212336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7707a40722a853bb7a6391a24e6e2a0bfb870a4e","tid":1304994,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:30:32.000Z","msg"